Tests can be found in :
src/test/java/com/herokuapp/computer_database/testFeatures/CRUD_feature.feature

Two things need to be installed on the running machine:
Java and Maven

- Configure the properties file to meet your needs: Like URLs credentials etc
/src/maim/resources/project.properties

- To run all the tests please use command:
```
mvn clean test
```
- To generate the report locally:
```
mvn allure:serve
```
- To generate the report to /target/site/allure-maven-plugin/index.html
```
mvn allure:report
```
